This UI kit will allow you to quickly build prototypes of your application.

The design system is made so that it is as convenient as possible for you to use components for your design projects. the ui kit is made in figma and contains more than 300 interface elements grouped using figma variants. The dimensions of all elements correspond to the guides material design.


  • 30 premade screens
  • Organized layers
  • Made with free fonts
  • Variants component system
  • 300+ customizable elements
  • Free icon pack
